<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Built for Fashion & Apparel</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Speed kills slow retailers.</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Fashion moves fast. Your POS needs to move faster — from rapid new-store rollouts to RFID self-checkout that gets Gen Z shoppers out the door in 32 seconds.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pillars-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);">
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon"><i class="ti ti-scan"></i></div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">RFID self-checkout — 62% faster</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc">32 seconds vs. 85 seconds traditional. Customers place items near the antenna — no barcode scanning, no line-of-sight required. Fast fashion consumers want choice and speed. Self-checkout gives them both. 30% of shoppers abandon if the wait exceeds 10 minutes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon"><i class="ti ti-arrows-exchange"></i></div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">Returns that build loyalty, not destroy it</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc">30–40% of online fashion is returned. 89% of shoppers stop buying after a difficult return. BORIS (Buy Online Return In Store) restocks inventory the moment an item comes back — available for the next walk-in right away, with no sync lag and no manual reconciliation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon"><i class="ti ti-package"></i></div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">Real-time inventory for short life cycles</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc">Collections turn over in weeks. <a href="/platform/inventory-control/" style="color: var(--brand-text);">RFID-powered inventory</a> ensures 99.9% accuracy across every store and channel. Eliminate overselling, prevent stockouts on trending items, and make BOPIS reliable for customers who expect the item to actually be there.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon"><i class="ti ti-rocket"></i></div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">Rapid store deployment</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc">Reiss deployed Teamwork's mobile POS across U.S. stores. City Beach expanded across Australia. 260 Sample Sale runs high-volume flash events with massive inventory churn on the same platform. The iOS interface reduces training to under 30 minutes and scales with brand expansion — pop-ups, flash sales, seasonal stores, and permanent flagships.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon"><i class="ti ti-infinity"></i></div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">Endless Aisle & BOPIS</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc">Out of stock in-store? Ship from another location in 3 taps. Buy online, pick up in store with RFID-verified stock. Ship-from-store turns every location into a micro-fulfillment center. Fashion has the highest click-and-collect rates of any vertical.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon"><i class="ti ti-user-heart"></i></div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">CRM & style-based loyalty</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc">Associates see purchase history, style preferences, and loyalty status in real time. The system surfaces <a href="/platform/121-commerce/" style="color: var(--brand-text);">personalized recommendations</a> and targeted offers based on browsing and buying patterns. 67% of Gen Z shoppers prioritize tech-driven experiences — give it to them.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

