        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Customers place items near the RFID antenna — the system detects every tagged item in seconds without barcode scanning or line-of-sight. Average transaction: 32 seconds vs. 85 seconds traditional (62% faster). Anti-bleed technology ensures only intended items register. This is critical for fashion retail where 30% of customers abandon checkout lines that exceed 10 minutes.</p></div>
